# UNICAMP-FT Thesis Standards and Templates

## Official Template Repository

The official thesis template is located in the `tese-ft-master` directory and should be used as the structural foundation:

- [tese.tex](mdc:templates_unicamp/tese-ft-master/tese.tex) - Main thesis document structure
- [tese-FT.cls](mdc:templates_unicamp/tese-ft-master/tese-FT.cls) - Official UNICAMP-FT LaTeX class file
- [compila.sh](mdc:templates_unicamp/tese-ft-master/compila.sh) - Compilation script for thesis
- [introducao.tex](mdc:templates_unicamp/tese-ft-master/introducao.tex) - Introduction template structure
- [desenvolvimento.tex](mdc:templates_unicamp/tese-ft-master/desenvolvimento.tex) - Development section template
- [conclusoes.tex](mdc:templates_unicamp/tese-ft-master/conclusoes.tex) - Conclusions template
- [bibliografia.bib](mdc:templates_unicamp/tese-ft-master/bibliografia.bib) - Bibliography format examples
- [DicasUteisTextosAcademicos.md](mdc:templates_unicamp/tese-ft-master/DicasUteisTextosAcademicos.md) - Academic writing tips

